********************************************************************************

Shortcuts for Image window
-----------------------

Left Arrow - move image to the right
Right Arrow - move image to the left
Up Arrow  - move image to the bottom
Down Arrow  - move image to the top
Plus/Minus - zoom Nx
Ctrl + Plus/Minus - zoom 2x or 0.5x
V - flip vertically
H - flip horizontally
Ctrl + Left Arrow - rotate left for N degrees
Ctrl + Right Arrow - rotate right for N degrees
Ctrl + Up/Down Arrow - rotate for 180 degrees up/down
Shift + Up/Down Arrow - rotate for 1 degree up/down
R - Reset
Space - next image
Backspace - previous image
Home - first image
End - last image
Esc,X,Return  - Close
P - Image properties
Q - Quick Browser
F - Fullscreen
T - Show/Hide toolbar with actions
[ - Hide toolbar with actions
] - Show toolbar with actions
Z - Show 'Zoom' menu
S - Show/Hide statusbar
1..9 - Zoom 1..9x
comma - Fit width
period - Fit height
*  - Fit image
slash - show help menu
L - "Ignore, if the image is less than window"
I - menu with images
A - stop/start animation (if animated, like GIF)
B - toggle drawing background for transparent images
E - show menu with external tools

F1 - First image from sequense
F2 - Previous
F3 - Next
F4 - Last

Use right mouse button to select zoom area!

Scroll - load next/prev file OR Zoom+/Zoom-
Shift + Scroll - Zoom+/Zoom-
Ctrl + Scroll - Zoom+ 2x/Zoom- 2x

******************

N - can be set through 'Options'
